{"tid":2256202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"協恩中學網上辦中一入學簡介會 校長冀學生懂自身在「家、國、社會」重要性","createTime":"2020-10-24T07:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T07:33:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"02c959af63841d189cf06cdce5a7dce720fd322b","tid":2256202,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:19:16.000Z","msg":"現在至11月正值直資中學招生高峰期，受疫情影響，普遍學校均採用網上形式進行講座。傳統直資名女校協恩中學今（24日）舉行網上中一入學簡介會，播放長個半小時的錄製片，不設即時提問環節，收看人數高峰期約630人。片段詳述課程、課外活動、收生程序等。校長梁少儀強調，協恩重視知識傳授與學術成果，她寄語家長，縱然期望女兒能學有所成，學校對「成功」的看法是「學生須找到學習、工作、生命的意義，成功時與人建立有意義的關係，懂得珍惜家人、尊重長輩同儕、扶持弱小，懂得知道自己在『家、國、社會』的重要性。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/IVWUE7P7INFB3PYUZCNDQVAT2U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2FIVWUE7P7INFB3PYUZCNDQVAT2U%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=cf800db7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2FIVWUE7P7INFB3PYUZCNDQVAT2U%2F&h=f17620d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/IVWUE7P7INFB3PYUZCNDQVAT2U/</a>"},{"pid":"5e524561a583d75796ede85cc33e1718cb21c45a","tid":2256202,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649275c7896208936404a809b495b26f66180e5e","tid":2256202,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:22:14.000Z","msg":"簡單講即係老屎忽成日講<br />\n讀好書，搵大錢，做國奴"},{"pid":"8389130f290c6bb3efc806299c1ddb5dfb7f376b","tid":2256202,"uid":83228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:28:12.000Z","msg":"家 國 社會<br />\n呢個順序<br />\n反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458c20e